    "title": {
      "rendered": "Bookmark Your Browsers! The Official Blogs of the World&#8217;s Most Popular Social Media Sites"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Most-Popular-Social-Media-Sites.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-17775\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Most-Popular-Social-Media-Sites-300x300.jpg?resize=300%2C300\" alt=\"Most Popular Social Media Sites\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Most-Popular-Social-Media-Sites.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Most-Popular-Social-Media-Sites.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Most-Popular-Social-Media-Sites.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Most-Popular-Social-Media-Sites.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Most-Popular-Social-Media-Sites.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>The nonprofit sector has a large community of technology bloggers committed to helping nonprofits\u00a0stay current on\u00a0emerging trends in social media, online fundraising, and mobile technology. There are these <strong><a href=\"http://www.themarketingpalette.com/#!35-resources-for-nonprofit-marketers/cyvb/5500c27b0cf27b8ab26c4c5d\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">35 nonprofit marketing blogs</a></strong>\u00a0and\u00a0these <a href=\"http://www.biztechmagazine.com/article/2015/03/25-must-read-nonprofit-it-blogs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>25 must-read nonprofit IT blogs</strong></a> as well as these <strong><a href=\"http://andreabrody.com/8-great-nonprofit-marketing-resources/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">8 great nonprofit resources</a></strong>. You can also browse 300+ on Twitter at\u00a0<strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/nonprofitorgs/lists/bloggers-resources\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@nonprofitorgs/lists/bloggers-resources</a></strong>. Reading the official blogs of the social media sites that we use most often is also useful and it may be time to add some new bookmarks to your browsers.</p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">1. Facebook Newsroom ::\u00a0<a href=\"http://newsroom.fb.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">newsroom.fb.com<br />\n</a><em>Facebook has 1.44 billion monthly users.<br />\n</em><a href=\"https://twitter.com/facebook\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@Facebook</a></h2>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://newsroom.fb.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17735\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Facebook-Stories.png?resize=600%2C316\" alt=\"Facebook Stories\" width=\"600\" height=\"316\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Facebook-Stories.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Facebook-Stories.png?resize=300%2C158&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></h3>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">2. YouTube Creator Blog\u00a0::\u00a0<a href=\"http://youtubecreator.blogspot.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">youtubecreator.blogspot.com</a><a href=\"http://newsroom.fb.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><br />\n</a><em>YouTube has 1 billion monthly users.<br />\n</em><a href=\"https://twitter.com/youtube\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@YouTube</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://youtube-global.blogspot.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17766\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/YouTube-Blog.png?resize=600%2C353\" alt=\"YouTube Blog\" width=\"600\" height=\"353\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/YouTube-Blog.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/YouTube-Blog.png?resize=300%2C176&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">3. LinkedIn Official Blog ::\u00a0<a href=\"http://blog.linkedin.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">blog.linkedin.com<br />\n</a><em>LinkedIn\u00a0has 347 million monthly users.<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/linkedin\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@LinkedIn</a></em><a href=\"http://blog.linkedin.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><br />\n</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://blog.linkedin.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17739\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/LinkedIn-Blog.png?resize=600%2C305\" alt=\"LinkedIn Blog\" width=\"600\" height=\"305\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/LinkedIn-Blog.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/LinkedIn-Blog.png?resize=300%2C152&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">4. Instagram Blog ::\u00a0<a href=\"http://blog.instagram.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">blog.instagram.com<br />\n</a><em>Instagram\u00a0has 300 million monthly users.<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/instagram\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@Instagram</a><br />\n</em></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://blog.instagram.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17745\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Instagram-Blog.png?resize=600%2C292\" alt=\"Instagram Blog\" width=\"600\" height=\"292\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Instagram-Blog.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Instagram-Blog.png?resize=300%2C146&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">5. Official Twitter\u00a0Blog ::\u00a0<a href=\"https://blog.twitter.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">blog.twitter.com</a><a href=\"http://blog.instagram.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><br />\n</a><em>Twitter\u00a0has 288 million monthly users.<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/twitter\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@Twitter</a><br />\n</em></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blog.twitter.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17747\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Twitter-Blog.png?resize=600%2C332\" alt=\"Twitter Blog\" width=\"600\" height=\"332\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Twitter-Blog.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Twitter-Blog.png?resize=300%2C166&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">6. Reddit\u00a0Blog\u00a0::\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.reddit.com/r/blog/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">reddit.com/r/blog</a><a href=\"http://blog.instagram.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><br />\n</a><em>Snapchat\u00a0has 174 million monthly users.<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/reddit\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@Reddit</a><br />\n</em></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.reddit.com/r/blog/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17757\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Reddit-Blog.png?resize=600%2C338\" alt=\"Reddit Blog\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Reddit-Blog.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Reddit-Blog.png?resize=300%2C169&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">7. Snapchat\u00a0Blog\u00a0::\u00a0<a href=\"http://blog.snapchat.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">blog.snapchat.com</a><a href=\"http://blog.instagram.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><br />\n</a><em>Snapchat\u00a0has 100\u00a0million monthly users.<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/snapchat\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@Snapchat</a><br />\n</em></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://blog.snapchat.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17754\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/SnapChat-Blog.png?resize=600%2C355\" alt=\"SnapChat Blog\" width=\"600\" height=\"355\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/SnapChat-Blog.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/SnapChat-Blog.png?resize=300%2C177&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">8. WordPress.org Blog ::\u00a0<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/news/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">wordpress.org/news<br />\n</a><em>WordPress.org\u00a0has 75\u00a0million monthly users.<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/wordpress\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@WordPress</a><br />\n</em></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/news/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17761\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/WordPress-Blog.png?resize=600%2C356\" alt=\"WordPress Blog\" width=\"600\" height=\"356\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/WordPress-Blog.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/WordPress-Blog.png?resize=300%2C178&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">9. Oh, How Pinteresting! Blog\u00a0::\u00a0<a href=\"http://blog.pinterest.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">blog.pinterest.com</a><a href=\"http://blog.instagram.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><br />\n</a><em>Pinterest\u00a0has 70\u00a0million monthly users.<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@Pinterest</a><br />\n</em></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Pinterest-Blog.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17750\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Pinterest-Blog.png?resize=600%2C311\" alt=\"Pinterest Blog\" width=\"600\" height=\"311\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Pinterest-Blog.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Pinterest-Blog.png?resize=300%2C155&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">10. Tumblr\u00a0Blog\u00a0::\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/about\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">tumblr.com/about</a><a href=\"http://blog.instagram.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><br />\n</a><em>Tumblr\u00a0has 50\u00a0million monthly users.<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/tumblr\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@Tumblr</a><br />\n</em></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/about\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17759\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Tumblr-Blog.png?resize=600%2C271\" alt=\"Tumblr Blog\" width=\"600\" height=\"271\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Tumblr-Blog.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Tumblr-Blog.png?resize=300%2C135&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">BONUS: Google for Nonprofits Blog ::<br />\n<a href=\"http://googlefornonprofits.blogspot.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">googlefornonprofits.blogspot.com</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/googlenonprofit\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@GoogleNonprofit</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://googlefornonprofits.blogspot.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17772\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Google-for-Nonprofits-Blog.png?resize=600%2C273\" alt=\"Google for Nonprofits Blog\" width=\"600\" height=\"273\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Google-for-Nonprofits-Blog.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Google-for-Nonprofits-Blog.png?resize=300%2C136&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<hr />\n<table style=\"border-color: transparent; width: 600px; background-color: #ffffff;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/social-and-mobile-media-webinars-for-nonprofits/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-17655\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/TWO.png?resize=299%2C167\" alt=\"TWO\" width=\"299\" height=\"167\" /></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/social-and-mobile-media-training-for-nonprofits/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-17656\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/ONE.png?resize=299%2C167\" alt=\"ONE\" width=\"299\" height=\"167\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n",
